{"tid":1999808,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[專業清算師] 核爆！英國SRA確認陳文慧並非英國事務律師！","createTime":"2020-05-03T12:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T12:06:03.000Z","uid":197256,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4144b52504dd4cecbe0923dea9fde3e5bfb7080f","tid":1999808,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:02:53.000Z","msg":"轉自 專業清算師 fb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/posts/256850365689074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi%2Fposts%2F256850365689074&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=f25e7b63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/posts/256850365689074</a><br />\n<br />\n手足任務：<br />\n(1) Tag全港所有傳媒＋海外傳媒<br />\n(2) 留言&ldquo;又一執葉律師&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n清算師團隊剛收到英國Solicitors Regulation Authority(SRA)書面確認陳文慧女士並非英國事務律師。同時，SRA已致函要求陳女士在香港大律師公會的介紹中停止自稱英國律師，並已就事件通報大律師公會。<br />\n<br />\n我等相信陳女士於香港大律師公會網頁上刊載的自我介紹可能已構成虛假陳述，我等已再度致函香港大律師公會，要求該會盡快就陳女士的失當行為進行調查，以重拾大眾對大律師專業的信心。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態嚴重，在陳女士專業資格、誠信均存疑的情況下，我等有理由質疑其作為外聘檢控官，以及任職律政司檢控官時有否公平、守法、合規地處理獲分配的檢控案件。我等希望陳文慧女士能向公眾就其行為一一交代，承擔作為「人」的基本責任。<br />\n<br />\n公開信已透過電郵發送至香港大律師公會，大家毋需重覆寄出，但絕對歡迎大家轉貼此帖；我們同時要求公會盡快作出調查及在有需要時轉交執法部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n第一擊(手足只需繼續幫手Share出去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244509196923191&amp;id=107843517256427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D244509196923191%26id%3D107843517256427&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=bb47d2f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244509196923191&amp;id=107843517256427</a><br />\n<br />\n第二擊(手足盡可能Share出去外國傳媒)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244986670208777&amp;id=107843517256427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D244986670208777%26id%3D107843517256427&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=e593802a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=244986670208777&amp;id=107843517256427</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明出處：清算師團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=2c4c09b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vendettists\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvendettists&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=62ac2ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vendettists</a><br />\n<br />\n#虛報資歷<br />\n#又一位執葉律師<br />\n#衰過狗<br />\n#到時比人告咪可以有righttobeheard囉"},{"pid":"7d96b6da467c39013c1673d7a0ccd16cc7b54fd5","tid":1999808,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"dddddd"},{"pid":"1ee12a43dc21646074c7168db7934f02b7bb4f7b","tid":1999808,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"2"}]}